✅ GamerSystem Installation Guide
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

1. 📥 Download Essentials

Get gamersystem.sk from our GitHub
(Check description for direct link)

2. ⚙️ Install Skript

Required base: Skript Plugin

➡️ Place JAR in your plugins folder

3. 🚀 Server Startup

Wait for full initialization

Verify Skript loads correctly

4. 📂 Install Script

markdown
plugins/
└── Skript/
    └── scripts/
        └── gamersystem.sk  ← Place here
5. 🔄 Activate System

bash
/skript reload gamersystem.sk
6. 🎮 Key Command

bash
/ess  # Shows all available features
⚠️ Important Notes

🔄 Always reload after updates

❌ Redistribution prohibited

📊 Supports Skript 2.6+

💡 Pro Tips

Type /ess help for commands

Check console for load confirmation

Backup before major updates

